05/09/2024

You can now define the exchange matrix directly if you have multi-modal motions
For instance, for 4 site hop dynamics the universal keyword: 

kex 1 1.0e9

Can be replaced by the explicit exchange matrix:

kex_mat 1 
-3.0e9 1.0e9 1.0e9 1.0e9
1.0e9 -3.0e9 1.0e9 1.0e9
1.0e9 1.0e9 -3.0e9 1.0e9
1.0e9 1.0e9 1.0e9 -3.0e9
